{"tid":2388632,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"「開心姐姐」取代麥當勞叔叔｜","createTime":"2021-01-31T09:30:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T04:28:15.000Z","uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7591f50ec421388a23db6defcb59fd6b6e55fef7","tid":2388632,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T09:30:52.000Z","msg":"開心姐姐」取代麥當勞叔叔更新時間 (HKT): 2021.01.08 02:00<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/pf/resources/images/icons/hk-appledaily/facebook-square.svg?d=187\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fpf%2Fresources%2Fimages%2Ficons%2Fhk-appledaily%2Ffacebook-square.svg%3Fd%3D187&h=210a6d88&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/pf/resources/images/icons/hk-appledaily/twitter-square.svg?d=187\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fpf%2Fresources%2Fimages%2Ficons%2Fhk-appledaily%2Ftwitter-square.svg%3Fd%3D187&h=5f5316b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/pf/resources/images/icons/hk-appledaily/link-square.svg?d=187\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fpf%2Fresources%2Fimages%2Ficons%2Fhk-appledaily%2Flink-square.svg%3Fd%3D187&h=73faeddd&s={SIZE}\" />AAA內地麥當勞繼改名「金拱門」後，近日又推出「二次元」新形象「開心姐姐」，與小朋友唱歌、跳舞和講故事。今年元旦起，正式宣傳新代言人「開心姐姐」，讓網民投票選出該二次元偶像暱稱。事件引起網民熱議，亦惹起經典代言人「麥當勞叔叔」引退疑雲。此外，也有眼利網民發現，「開心姐姐」設計與日本2016年出道的虛擬偶像「絆愛」相似，質疑有抄襲之嫌。<br />\n[url=<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3XzbUj5ovHeo4w1D1zrjCoW37T4=/2107x1181/filters:quality\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3XzbUj5ovHeo4w1D1zrjCoW37T4%3D%2F2107x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWqd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=f45e669b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3XzbUj5ovHeo4w1D1zrjCoW37T4%3D%2F2107x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality&h=e4ca6379\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3XzbUj5ovHeo4w1D1zrjCoW37T4=/2107x1181/filters:quality</a>(100)/<a href=\"http://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/E5LSMNPUSNFDJE24XYRIFBYEWI.jpg]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FE5LSMNPUSNFDJE24XYRIFBYEWI.jpg%5D&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWqd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=00472309\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/E5LSMNPUSNFDJE24XYRIFBYEWI.jpg]</a><img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pYBafJrTi-05D0-GTcp3KxdJI0c=/802x449/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/E5LSMNPUSNFDJE24XYRIFBYEWI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpYBafJrTi-05D0-GTcp3KxdJI0c%3D%2F802x449%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FE5LSMNPUSNFDJE24XYRIFBYEWI.jpg&h=a608d88f&s={SIZE}\" />■內地麥當勞推出新代言人「開心姐姐」。互聯網[/url]疑抄日虛擬偶像「絆愛」<br />\n2017年中資「中信資本」取得內地麥當勞大部份股份後，改名「金拱門（中國）有限公司」。今次推出的二次元新代言人開心姐姐，有指是來自麥當勞為小朋友慶祝生日派對，穿着粉紅色衣服、頭戴同色髮帶的女店員。據官方網站介紹，開心姐姐身高165厘米、摩羯座、1月1日生日、是一名唱跳偶像，微信上的麥當勞應用程式可搜尋到開心姐姐，她會向小朋友示範跳舞、為小朋友的舞蹈打分及講故事等。<br />\n麥當勞過往代言人中，麥當勞叔叔最家喻戶曉，1990年代麥當勞叔叔身邊，有漢堡神偷、滑嘟嘟、小飛飛等，是不少人童年回憶。惟後來麥當勞調整經營策略，一眾卡通代言人淡出。有分析指，今次內地麥當勞推出開心姐姐，有意吸引兒童及年輕消費者。<br />\n官方為開心姐姐的暱稱投票，「金開心」、「樂小悠」、「金小兮」三個選項中，「金開心」最為熱門。有人則認為，與其取名為與「金拱門」一樣老土的「金開心」，不如索性改名為「金拱姬」、「麥香姬」等；亦有網民期望麥當勞叔叔回歸。<br />\n翻查內地麥當勞官方網站，仍有關麥當勞叔叔描述，並稱其為麥當勞的「首席快樂官」。至於麥當勞官方微博，麥當勞叔叔上次帖文，是去年12月29日。"},{"pid":"27f1c68df66c07c3be5d3a49467c37b829e6feca","tid":2388632,"uid":236505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:28:15.000Z","msg":"支那人抄開野<br />\n改個名都特別冇創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}